class  CommandParser
 The command Parser and dispatcher for PaymentItems commands The command handelers input is in a noun (refering to the class) and a verb referring to the method. This class users reflection to determine the paramters to parse and pass to the PaymentItem. Each input type for a method has a method to parese the PaymentCommand arguments for the correct input variables. The output is the XML result returned from the invoked PaymentItem command. More...
